question: Who were the Wright Brothers?
subject: web_search
derived_ev: The Wright brothers are identified as Orville Wright (August 19, 1871 – January 30, 1948) and Wilbur Wright (April 16, 1867 – May 30, 1912) according to Wikipedia
The National Air and Space Museum confirms Wilbur and Orville Wright as universally recognized aviation pioneers
The Wright Brothers are Orville and Wilbur Wright
